    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrated sufficient fidelity for predicting relative hemolysis index across the clinical operating range. The 6 non-assessed factors are not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
